\viewkind4\uc1\f0\fs24\b\fs32 FSI Digital - 12-Week Structured Training & Hiring Curriculum\b0\fs24\par\par
\b 1. Executive Summary\b0\par
This template is designed to satisfy the requirement of Youth Employment and Canada Job Grant programs proving the structured, high-value nature of the planned hire.\par\par
\b 2. Role Definition & Core Milestones\b0\par
Role Title: Intermediate Technical Specialist / Apprentice.
Onboarding Period: Weeks 1-4. Focus: Core systems overview, security compliance protocols.
Advancement Period: Weeks 5-8. Focus: Supervised task execution, API mapping, data migrations.
Independence Milestone: Weeks 9-12. Focus: Unsupervised delivery, quality assurance sign-offs.\par\par
\b 3. Technical Training curriculum\b0\par
Week 1-2: Security guidelines, cloud architecture setups, coding framework orientation.
Week 3-4: Local testing suites configuration, database migration patterns validation.
Week 5-8: Production hot-fixes monitoring, client tickets analysis.
Week 9-12: Complete sprint cycles execution.\par\par
